<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 08:10:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>21名士兵丧生，这是以色列自加沙地面进攻开始以来最严重的事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-live/three-israeli-officers-killed-in-southern-gaza-strip-combat/0000018d-345d-d6df-adcf-35dd49d60000</link><description>以色列军队在加沙边境附近拆除建筑物。哈马斯枪手向附近的一辆坦克发射火箭弹，同时发生爆炸，导致建筑物倒塌，里面有士兵。 据报道，以色列通过调解人向哈马斯提出了一项建议，其中包括暂停战斗长达两个月据 Axios 报道，作为新协议的一部分 ■ 胡塞武装声称使用海军导弹袭击了一艘“美国海军货船”</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 03:34:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-live/three-israeli-officers-killed-in-southern-gaza-strip-combat/0000018d-345d-d6df-adcf-35dd49d60000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列官员因涉嫌向巴勒斯坦人出售数千份入境许可证而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/three-israeli-officers-arrested-on-suspicion-of-selling-entry-permits-to-palestinians/0000018d-333e-d6df-adcf-33bf7c6d0000</link><description>两名主要嫌疑人是一名职业军官和他的父亲，警方在他的家中发现了 74 万谢克尔现金和 121 块金锭</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 22:25:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/three-israeli-officers-arrested-on-suspicion-of-selling-entry-permits-to-palestinians/0000018d-333e-d6df-adcf-33bf7c6d0000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，内塔尼亚胡告诉人质家属：以色列愿意为新协议做出让步</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-reportedly-told-hostages-families-israel-would-make-concessions-for-new-deal/0000018d-332d-d81e-abdf-3b2dcf850000</link><description>消息人士称，总理似乎愿意在释放巴勒斯坦囚犯的数量和身份问题上做出妥协——300人在内塔尼亚胡耶路撒冷的家外示威</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 22:08:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-reportedly-told-hostages-families-israel-would-make-concessions-for-new-deal/0000018d-332d-d81e-abdf-3b2dcf850000</guid></item><item><title>周一，三名以色列国防军军官在加沙战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/three-israeli-army-officers-killed-in-gaza-combat-on-monday/0000018d-328a-d81e-abdf-3a8e3dfe0000</link><description>这三人分别是大卫·纳蒂·阿尔法西少校、伊莱·利维少校和埃亚尔·梅沃拉奇·特维托上尉，均在加沙地带南部的一场战斗中阵亡。据军方称，自地面行动开始以来，已有200名以色列士兵在加沙丧生</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 19:38:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/three-israeli-army-officers-killed-in-gaza-combat-on-monday/0000018d-328a-d81e-abdf-3a8e3dfe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外长通过视频回避欧盟关于两国解决方案的讨论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/israels-foreign-minister-evades-eu-discussion-on-two-state-solution-with-video-show/0000018d-32a4-db8f-a7df-32f7bc410000</link><description>以色列外长以色列·卡茨在访问布鲁塞尔期间参加了中东问题的讨论</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 19:34:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/israels-foreign-minister-evades-eu-discussion-on-two-state-solution-with-video-show/0000018d-32a4-db8f-a7df-32f7bc410000</guid></item><item><title>埃隆·马斯克与本·夏皮罗在奥斯维辛：又一场愤世嫉俗的粉饰表演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-22/ty-article/.highlight/elon-musk-with-ben-shapiro-in-auschwitz-another-cynical-whitewashing-performance/0000018d-326b-db8f-a7df-32fb97df0000</link><description>马斯克从这些展示中得到的好处是显而易见的，但对欧洲犹太协会等东道主来说有什么好处就不言而喻了</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 19:14:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-22/ty-article/.highlight/elon-musk-with-ben-shapiro-in-auschwitz-another-cynical-whitewashing-performance/0000018d-326b-db8f-a7df-32fb97df0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管因以色列与哈马斯战争而取消航班，本古里安机场的乘客数量仍增加了 10%</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/number-of-passengers-at-ben-gurion-airport-rises-10-despite-israel-hamas-war/0000018d-3246-d81e-abdf-3a4e9e540000</link><description>虽然大多数外国航空公司决定停止或限制往返以色列的航班，但 2022 年至 2023 年间乘客总数增加了 10%</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 19:13:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/number-of-passengers-at-ben-gurion-airport-rises-10-despite-israel-hamas-war/0000018d-3246-d81e-abdf-3a4e9e540000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队：汗尤尼斯的激烈战斗预计将持续数天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-intense-fighting-in-khan-yunis-expected-to-last-several-days/0000018d-3215-d81e-abdf-3a1d5a440000</link><description>汗尤尼斯是加沙南部最大的城市，也是哈马斯的据点，最近几周一直是战斗中心。数以千计的平民使日益激烈的战斗变得更加复杂，以色列鼓励他们向南迁移到拉法</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 18:41:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-intense-fighting-in-khan-yunis-expected-to-last-several-days/0000018d-3215-d81e-abdf-3a1d5a440000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡已经没有谎言了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-running-out-of-lies/0000018d-31d5-d81e-abdf-39dda0270000</link><description>总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡面临的两大压力——呼吁达成人质协议和美国针对加沙的“事后”计划——正变得难以承受。他们即将向他汇合</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 17:37:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-running-out-of-lies/0000018d-31d5-d81e-abdf-39dda0270000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和美国正在就两国解决方案进行虚假辩论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-and-the-u-s-are-engaging-in-a-bogus-debate-over-the-two-state-solution/0000018d-3176-d81e-abdf-397e98c40000</link><description>美国对与以色列一起建立巴勒斯坦国的前景的关注是内塔尼亚胡精心策划的策略的一部分，内塔尼亚胡又故技重施。两国解决方案现在不可能实现，拜登政府知道这一点</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 17:25:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-and-the-u-s-are-engaging-in-a-bogus-debate-over-the-two-state-solution/0000018d-3176-d81e-abdf-397e98c40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部长威胁起诉《国土报》，称其在恐怖袭击后“在鲜血上跳舞”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-threatens-to-sue-haaretz-for-saying-he-was-dancing-on-blood/0000018d-31cb-d81e-abdf-39cfd0700000</link><description>尤阿夫·基什（Yoav Kisch）在谈到拉阿纳纳恐怖袭击后《国土报》发表的两篇文章时表示，“将教育部长描绘成在死者和伤者的鲜血上跳舞的人构成了严重的诽谤”。他的律师要求《国土报》删除这些文章并道歉</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 17:22:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-threatens-to-sue-haaretz-for-saying-he-was-dancing-on-blood/0000018d-31cb-d81e-abdf-39cfd0700000</guid></item><item><title>拒绝哈马斯条件后第二天，内塔尼亚胡告诉人质家属“没有真正的提议”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tells-hostage-families-no-proposal-on-the-table-day-after-rejecting-hamas-terms/0000018d-31c3-db8f-a7df-33f30b810000</link><description>以色列总理在一次会议上对人质家属说，哈马斯没有提出真正的提议——这不是真的。一天前，他声称自己拒绝了哈马斯提出的协议，因为接受该协议意味着“我们的士兵将白白死去</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 16:15:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tells-hostage-families-no-proposal-on-the-table-day-after-rejecting-hamas-terms/0000018d-31c3-db8f-a7df-33f30b810000</guid></item><item><title>以色列改革运动请愿反对不教授核心课程的学校</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-reform-movement-petitions-against-schools-that-do-not-teach-core-curriculum/0000018d-3177-d81e-abdf-397f10b30000</link><description>以色列宗教行动中心提交了请愿书，涉及所谓“豁免”的极端正统机构，这些机构只需教授 55% 的核心课程</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 14:59:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-reform-movement-petitions-against-schools-that-do-not-teach-core-curriculum/0000018d-3177-d81e-abdf-397f10b30000</guid></item><item><title>“当他们在加沙死去时，你不会坐在这里”：人质家庭冲击以色列议会委员会会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/you-wont-sit-here-while-theyre-dying-hostage-families-storm-knesset-committee-meeting/0000018d-3110-d268-addd-3b7909ac0000</link><description>沙查尔·莫尔的叔叔在加沙被哈马斯关押，他呼吁摩西·加夫尼和其他以色列议会极端正统派议员离开政府</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 14:55:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/you-wont-sit-here-while-theyre-dying-hostage-families-storm-knesset-committee-meeting/0000018d-3110-d268-addd-3b7909ac0000</guid></item><item><title>两名东耶路撒冷居民因涉嫌在以色列议会附近策划受 ISIS 启发的恐怖阴谋而被起诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/two-east-jerusalem-residents-indicted-for-aledged-isis-inspired-terror-plot-near-knesset/0000018d-318e-d268-addd-3bffc8a70000</link><description>根据起诉书，这两个人在网上被激进化并宣誓效忠伊斯兰国后，据称计划于 11 月在议会外炸毁一辆装满油箱的卡车。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 14:45:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/two-east-jerusalem-residents-indicted-for-aledged-isis-inspired-terror-plot-near-knesset/0000018d-318e-d268-addd-3bffc8a70000</guid></item><item><title>新民意调查显示，以色列人对拜登将巴勒斯坦国与释放人质、沙特关系正常化联系起来的计划持开放态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/poll-israelis-open-to-biden-plan-linking-palestinian-state-hostages-saudi-normalization/0000018d-3035-dd75-addd-f2f577900000</link><description>尽管人们假设以色列人自 10 月 7 日起就会向右转，但最近的一项民意调查显示，如果建立一个非军事化的巴勒斯坦国与释放人质和沙特关系正常化一起成为一揽子协议的一部分，大多数人将支持建立非军事化的巴勒斯坦国。这对拜登来说是个好消息</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 13:18:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/poll-israelis-open-to-biden-plan-linking-palestinian-state-hostages-saudi-normalization/0000018d-3035-dd75-addd-f2f577900000</guid></item><item><title>如果没有巴勒斯坦工人，以色列经济还能持续多久？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-wont-let-palestinian-workers-in-but-its-economy-needs-them-desperately/0000018d-2bda-dd75-addd-fbfb543a0000</link><description>自加沙战争开始以来，政府已对估计 120,000 名巴勒斯坦工人关闭了大门，但尚未提出用外国工人取代他们的计划 ■ 与此同时，失去相当一部分劳动力的企业主正在付出代价</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 13:15:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-wont-let-palestinian-workers-in-but-its-economy-needs-them-desperately/0000018d-2bda-dd75-addd-fbfb543a0000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，数十名巴勒斯坦人在汗尤尼斯的战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/idf-deepens-khan-yunis-invasion-palestinians-report-dozens-killed-including-children/0000018d-30c4-d81e-abdf-38ccc2c20000</link><description>巴勒斯坦红新月会反驳说，以色列国防军阻止他们到达被轰炸的地区，包括医疗中心。以色列军队表示，部队“继续打击汗尤尼斯地区的恐怖分子目标”</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 13:04:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/idf-deepens-khan-yunis-invasion-palestinians-report-dozens-killed-including-children/0000018d-30c4-d81e-abdf-38ccc2c20000</guid></item><item><title>你会让你的孩子参加内塔尼亚胡的战争吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/would-you-send-your-child-to-fight-in-netanyahus-war/0000018d-30a6-dd75-addd-f2e7ec590000</link><description>每个人都必须问自己，他们是否会去对抗哈马斯，或者将他们的孩子送去参加这场他们可能一去不复返的战争</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 11:59:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/would-you-send-your-child-to-fight-in-netanyahus-war/0000018d-30a6-dd75-addd-f2e7ec590000</guid></item><item><title>他被绑架到加沙并被以色列士兵杀害。他的乐队成员为他而演奏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-01-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bandmates-of-israeli-drummer-kidnapped-by-hamas-and-killed-by-idf-play-on-in-his-honor/0000018d-2bea-dd75-addd-fbeb4ef90000</link><description>10 月 7 日 Yotam Haim 被哈马斯绑架的那天，他和他的金属核乐队 Persephore 即将举行他们有史以来最盛大的演出。他的乐队成员回忆起一位敏感的鼓手，他教会他们要有远大的梦想，同时成功地战胜了内心的恶魔</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 11:38:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-01-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bandmates-of-israeli-drummer-kidnapped-by-hamas-and-killed-by-idf-play-on-in-his-honor/0000018d-2bea-dd75-addd-fbeb4ef90000</guid></item></channel></rss>